Customer: Hello.

Customer: Haan ji, haan ji.
Executive: Ji, sir, main Priyanshu baat kar raha tha. Aapka account manager IndiaMART head office se. 
Customer: Haan, bolo. Wo, wo sir, kal maine sir ko bhi call kiya tha. Wo aapke yahan se ek mail aaya tha IndiaMART pe. Maine mail kiya hua hai. Achcha ji. Kya kya hai ji? Mere ko maine abhi payment kar diya, mere ko koi inquiry nahi aa rahi hai. Koi leads bhi nahi aa rahe, pura khali khali ja raha hai.
Executive: Achcha ji. Ji, usi ke liye sir maine call kiya tha. Matlab domestic mein ye issue aa raha hai ya export mein aa raha hai?
Customer: Export mein, export mein. Domestic ka kuch nahi hai. Export ka. Export ka aa raha hai. Export mein matlab jo direct direct inquiry aati thi, wahan problem hai ya buyleads mein sir? Direct inquiry aati hi nahi thi. Direct to koi aa hi nahi mere ko. Mere ko jo bhi buylead main purchase karta hu, buylead bhi nahi aa rahi koi.
Executive: Achcha, ek second main check kar raha hu. Line pe rahiyega aap. Wahi maine kal bhi do teen baar kiya. Maine kaha puchu maine sir ka to pehle sahi chala tha ki jaldi ye problem aayi nahi. Abhi kafi time baad sir ne ye problem. Pehle to unki badi bahut achcha tha. Ye payment karne ke baad hi ab lapda ho gaya.
Executive: Nahi nahi, aisa wo payment ka usse koi wo nahi hai sir. Wo to hum log ka har saal hi hota hai. Ye dekhiye main ek baar bata de raha hu hum log ka export mein. Hmm.
Executive: Jayco Industries. Foreign. Ko abhi to matlab October se ye problem aayi hai aapko na? Last month se?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan, keh rahe last month se ye problem aayi hai sir October se aapko?
Customer: Haan, matlab ye do char hafte se aisa issue hai matlab leads hi nahi aa pa rahi hai.
Executive: Idhar aapka haan October mein lead aapki thodi si kam bhi use hui hai. Baki usse pehle to theek tha. Isme jo buylead approval hai na sir usme aisa kuch khas to difference nahi hai. Haan ye hai jo abhi main yahan pe dekh raha hu last ek saal ka graph to abhi November December se thoda sa demand badhta hai aapke product mein bahar ki countries mein. Demand bahut badh gaya hai. Abhi to demand badh gaya kaam itna hai ki pucho mat lekin lead bilkul nahi hai aapki.
Executive: Ye aapka screen leads aayegi kyuki sir abhi main dekh raha hu isi month mein aisa hi keh lo aap is month mein demand apna badhta hai. Last month mein hua kya na thoda sa buylead aapke paas jo buylead approve hota tha hamare yahan ye 55, 54, 40, 45 aise rehta tha 50 ke aas pass around. Abhi jo last month 35 buylead ka ye approval raha hai. Matlab buylead bhi thodi si kam generate hui hai to ye reason bhi raha hoga ki aapko buylead kam mil paye. to mere account mein do ya teen hi dikhti hai. Mere ko do teen hi dikhta hai.
Executive: Achcha. Nahi buyleads ke kya hai na jaise thoda to 10 se 12 ek minute bhaiya ji. Haan.
Customer: Do hi buylead dikh raha hai abhi bhi.
Executive: Haan, abhi dekha maine do dikha raha hai. Kenya ka dikha raha hai aur Nepal ka. Haan bas. Wo bhi mere apna iska nahi hai alag hi kisi kuch matlab hi kuch dikha raha hai wo. Mere product ke relevant bhi nahi hai wo.
Executive: Ji nahi, pichle mahine ka to mujhe dikh raha hai sir hum log ka kya hai jo buylead hi apne paas aaya na IndiaMART ke paas wo 10 se 12 buylead normal month ke compare mein kam aaya hai to aapka use bhi kam hi hua hai is vajah se. Aap jo use kar rahe the wo normal 30, 40, 50, 55 aise buylead jata tha wo pichle mahine keval 26 hi buylead reh gaya aapka jo aapne use kiya pure mahine mein. Yani ki buylead use hua hai kam kyuki buylead total aaya kam hai. Jo buylead hamare paas 45, 50, 54 aata tha export ka wo buylead 35 aaya keval. To isi vajah se aapke paas bhi sir wo kam gaya. Matlab apne koi catalog mein issue nahi aaya hai wo export ki inquiry hi kam generate hui hai aapko main ek baar screenshot bhi bhej dunga is cheez ka. Aap dekhiyega to ye impact kyuki aapko maine kal kal jab call kiya tha na to kal main pehle pura catalog hi check kar raha tha sir maine kaha dekhiye yahan pe kahin koi aisa to nahi koi setting mein hai koi cheez agar galat ho gayi ho jis vajah se impact aa raha ho kyuki mail pe likha hua tha ki inquiry kam hui hai aapki jo aapne mujhe bheja tha. Haan main wahi hai. Ji. Ji to isme maine iske pehle phone kiya tha wo fir HR madam madam ko ne koi madam ko usko phone kiya tha haan main karwa rahi hu main chutti par hu main karwa rahi hu fir bhi kuch hua nahi.
Executive: Achcha wo mam ko kiya tha to aapke paas mera number nahi hai sir Priyanshu naam hai mera? Itne sare number se na pata nahi yaar wo. Achcha koi baat nahi suniye main nahi mam ko bhi keh sakte hain abhi wo office aa gayi hain actually kya tha Diwali ke baad unke yahan chhat puja rehti hai to 29 30 tarikh tak seedha 30 tarikh ko hui ki sham ko wo aayi hain yahan pe. To abhi to wo bhi office mein unko bhi karenge aur main aapko abhi whatsapp pe apna number bhi bhej de raha hu. Abhi kya hai ji abhi wo catalog maine pura ek baar check kiya tha dobara se main dekh lunga kahin koi minor aisa to nahi mistake ho aur jo main reason raha na sir wo yahi raha ki buylead hamare paas kam generate hui hai aur abhi is time se season badha bhi hai kyuki main dekh raha hu har saal is time pe demand jyada rehti hai to abhi apne paas bhi ye badhega. Theek hai aur aap aur main aur ho sakta hai main aapko fir do din mein teen din mein ek baar feedback lunga isi cheez ke liye apne direct number se to aap mujhe batayega. Chalega. Ji aur sir haan aur sir ek cheez aur jaise ye customer care pe apne mail kiya tha na to ek yahan pe feedback ka wo open ho jata hai to main use close karunga to ek aapke paas abhi feedback ke liye mail jayega to us pe aap mere liye jayega wo mere ko feedback de dijiyega. kar paunga usko main kal hi reply karunga main side pe aaya hu. Achcha side pe hai to theek hai sir kal agar kijiyega to us pe positive feedback aap dijiyega baki main aapko abhi whatsapp pe details bhej raha hu to hum connect rahenge har do teen din mein ek baar feedback lenge jab tak ye sahi nahi ho jata. Theek hai. Theek hai thank you sir.
